satisfied and have left plenty; for Jehovah has blessed his people; and
what is left is this great store.

<span id="an_31:11">31:11</span> And Hezekiah commanded to prepare
chambers in the house of Jehovah; and they prepared \[them\],

<span id="an_31:12">31:12</span> and brought in the heave-offerings and
the tithes and the dedicated things faithfully; and over these Cononiah
