<span id="an_32:10">32:10</span> Thus says Sennacherib king of Assyria:
On what do ye rely that ye abide in the siege in Jerusalem?

<span id="an_32:11">32:11</span> Does not Hezekiah persuade you, to give
yourselves over to die by famine and by thirst, saying, Jehovah our God
