out of my hand?

<span id="an_32:16">32:16</span> And his servants spoke yet more against
Jehovah, the \[true\] God, and against his servant Hezekiah.

<span id="an_32:17">32:17</span> And he wrote a letter to rail at
Jehovah the God of Israel, and to speak against him saying, As the gods
