<span id="an_32:29">32:29</span> And he provided for himself cities, and
possessions of flocks and herds in abundance; for God gave him very much
substance.

<span id="an_32:30">32:30</span> And he, Hezekiah, stopped the upper
outlet of the waters of Gihon, and brought it straight down to the west
side of the city of David. And Hezekiah prospered in all his works.

<span id="an_32:31">32:31</span> However in \[the matter of\] the
